00:41:35.800 --> 00:41:38.307
and the only thing that
changes is the number,

00:41:38.783 --> 00:41:43.505
so we have to tell to announce
everything inside the container.

00:41:44.735 --> 00:41:49.973
And that's with "aria-atomic" is true.

00:41:54.027 --> 00:41:55.991
Then everything is announced.

00:41:56.015 --> 00:41:57.380
