The id is total, and it's read only,

00:43:27.519 --> 00:43:29.640
and has an initial value of 10.

00:43:30.434 --> 00:43:31.450
Right.

00:43:32.085 --> 00:43:35.871
In your use case, or form,
this may be far more complex,

00:43:36.529 --> 00:43:39.083
but I just want to show you the basics.

00:43:39.384 --> 00:43:42.139
So you can think about if
this way may be better for you.

00:43:42.718 --> 00:43:44.373
So, how does this work?

00:43:44.833 --> 00:43:49.548
There's a field added, "total price" 
and initial value of 10.

